N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 93.1 - To whom this part applies

State Regulations

This Part applies to professional fund raisers, fund raising counsel, professional
solicitors and commercial co-venturers, as defined in article 7-A, section 171-a; provided, however, that this Part shall not apply to any individual
or entity that prints, prepares for mailing and/or mails solicitation material but does not otherwise provide advice to or solicit on behalf of a
charitable organization. Notes
